# Tech Stack

## Web Framework

- I am using Next.js 15 with React 19

## Backend

- I am using resend for emails @https://resend.com

- I am using better-auth for authentication @https://better-auth.com

## Frontend

- I am using shadcn ui components from @https://ui.shadcn.com

- I am using Tanstack Table to display complex data @https://tanstack.com/table/latest/docs/introduction

- I am using Tanstack Query to handle requests @https://tanstack.com/query/latest/docs/framework/react/overview

## Database

- I am using Prisma as ORM @https://www.prisma.io/docs

- I am using Neon to host a postgres database @https://neon.tech

- I am using Zenstack to enhance prisma and automatically generate api routes for database and frontend queries for those api routes @https://zenstack.dev/docs/welcome
